      "description": "This FD3S chassis remains an analog masterpiece, featuring the legendary 13B-REW rotary engine with its sequential twin-turbocharged configuration intact and functioning with surgical precision. The factory-spec forced induction system delivers a linear power band, while the five-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement. Benefiting from a meticulously preserved double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential, the handling remains razor-sharp. This example boasts a pristine exterior with factory-original paint depth and an interior free of UV degradation or bolster wear. Mechanically, the compression numbers are optimal, ensuring the apex seals are in peak operating condition. A true collector-grade specimen for the rotary purist.",
